  <description type="morphology">Leaf blades 3–12(–18) cm × 5–25(–35+) mm. Involucres 12–15+ mm. Cypselae: bodies 4–5+ mm, beaks 0–1 mm; pappi 7–9(–12+) mm. 2n = 18.</description>
  <description type="phenology">Flowering Jun–Sep.</description>
  <description type="habitat">Calcareous sites, clearings in forests or shrublands, meadows, roadsides, stream banks, other wet sites;</description>
